description:
                      The UnderGarden MULTi3-ALiAS









Plot:

Challenge your mind in the wondrous depths of The UnderGarden. Plunge into a unique new world exploring large underground caverns, encountering mysterious creatures to befriend or avoid. Solve mind-bending brainteasers and puzzles as soothing tunes accompany you on your journey through 20 distinct levels of state of the art 3D graphics. The UnderGarden offers a mental challenge and aesthetic experience like nothing else.




NFO:

Release Group: ALiAS

Release Name: The.UnderGarden.MULTi3-ALiAS

Release Date: 11-11-2010

Filename: The.UnderGarden.MULTi3-ALiAS

Size: 257 MB

Type: Adventure

Developer: ATARI

Publisher: ATARI




Features

-Casual Zen game design offers 20 different levels, each with a unique look.
-The world springs to life with vibrant color and serene music as the player drifts past dormant seeds.
-Puzzles are physics based, solved by placing grown &quot;fruit&quot; that weighs down levers, or lifts up platforms to allow access to new areas.
-Progress is driven by player's own pace, desire to see their effect on the world, and exploration of new environments.
-First game of its type to offer 2 player co-op play.




Setup NFO:

1. Unrar
2. Run Setup.bat
3. Switch the language using setEN.bat or setDE.bat
4. Run the game with thUndergarden.exe
5. Have Fun


NOTES: When needed install dotNetFx35setup.exe and vcredistx86.exe


Support the software developers. If you like this game, BUY IT


